37/* Entry i contains (i!/2^t) where t is chosen such that the parenthesis
38 is an odd integer. */
39const mp_limb_t __gmp_oddfac_table[] = { ONE_LIMB_ODD_FACTORIAL_TABLE, ONE_LIMB_ODD_FACTORIAL_EXTTABLE };
40
41/* Entry i contains ((2i+1)!!/2^t) where t is chosen such that the parenthesis
42 is an odd integer. */
43const mp_limb_t __gmp_odd2fac_table[] = { ONE_LIMB_ODD_DOUBLEFACTORIAL_TABLE };
44
45/* Entry i contains 2i-popc(2i). */
46const unsigned char __gmp_fac2cnt_table[] = { TABLE_2N_MINUS_POPC_2N };
47
48const mp_limb_t __gmp_limbroots_table[] = { NTH_ROOT_NUMB_MASK_TABLE };
